============================================================
PART 4: GAUSS SUM FACTORIZATION (CORRECTED)
============================================================
g(a) = chi(a)*sqrt(p) at p=3 mod 4
g(a)*g(b) = chi(ab)*p

TRUE_deg2(D^{2n}) / (chi(ab)*p) should reveal the sign mechanism

