============================================================
PART 5: FULL H_HAT DECOMPOSITION BY TRACE POWER
============================================================
h_hat[{a,b}] = sum_{k even} weight_k * (1/k) * deg2(tr(A^k))
where deg2(tr(A^k)) = sum_n coeff_{k,n} * deg2(sum_freq D^{2n})

For circulant tournament, this simplifies to understanding
deg2(sum_freq D^{2n}) for each n.

